### 1. Add a Product to Inventory
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sku": "KEY-001",
    "name": "Mechanical Keyboard",
    "price": 75.50,
    "stockQuantity": 5,
    "minThreshold": 3
}

###

### 2. Process a Sales Order (Sell 3 Keyboards)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orderType": "OUTBOUND",
    "productId": 1,
    "quantity": 3
}

###

### 3. Check for Low Stock Alerts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/alerts/low-stock
